{"tid":2013268,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強：外籍人士日前被捕後死亡的事件 同事全部根據規矩 看不到有做得不好地方","createTime":"2020-05-12T07:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T13:32:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4924951e1275be8f9904755b7dc9910f84c268","tid":2013268,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:40:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525684-20200512.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525684-20200512.htm&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmDBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=0ea264fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525684-20200512.htm&h=99712d79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525684-20200512.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警務處處長鄧炳強出席元朗區議會會議時說，一名外籍人士日前被捕後死亡的事件，同事全部根據規矩工作，暫時看不到有做得不好的地方。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強回應議員提問時指，該名人士在街上行為失常、打爛東西，警方接報後與兩名途人制服他，由於對方精神異常，因此召喚救護車將他送院後於翌日離世。初步醫療報告顯示，死者沒有骨折，但要詳細檢視驗屍報告才能確定死因，相信會召開死因庭處理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，鄧炳強表示，一名女子早前聲稱在警署遭強姦的案件，律政司已指示警方以涉嫌給予假口供拘捕對方，但她目前已經潛逃，正被警方通緝。"},{"pid":"20d1233001b0747e13755929111d3c0095ad80fb","tid":2013268,"uid":47081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"PK鄧：外藉人士抵死"},{"pid":"ad2cbb4066aab54755c6ad21a1ae140ed8a8d131","tid":2013268,"uid":49669,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"根據黑警守則，打死人都可以話跟足規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4960bdd4e29dd8402e944baad111bd6a65507f","tid":2013268,"uid":107405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"我班馬仔永遠無錯 你地比人打死都係你地唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e972d5d697ba1bf278a6810aee59abbb02cb59e8","tid":2013268,"uid":65604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T0